{"tid":1273287,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"受傷的人請入黎（詳細版）","createTime":"2019-07-01T13:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T13:55:48.000Z","uid":264331,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4483eecf848763a573d10e61957d725c2dab6783","tid":1273287,"uid":264331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:55:48.000Z","msg":"止血方法<br />\n(1) 用無菌紗布按壓傷口，係緊急情況，用乾淨的布及衣服都可以！<br />\n(2) 止血之後，用生理鹽水/清水慢慢抺走止血用的紗布<br />\n<br />\n洗傷口用具<br />\n(1)無菌敷料包<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r538EhG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr538EhG.png&h=741aff13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(2)洗傷口藥水<br />\n(3)無菌紗布<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rjfu8bi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frjfu8bi.png&h=99819071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(4)Micropore<br />\n(5)垃圾袋<br />\n<br />\nSodium chloride 生理鹽水<br />\n洗一般傷口<br />\n濕潤舊敷料，方便掀起，唔好扯舊敷料<br />\n<br />\nUnisept 洗傷口藥水 （紅色）<br />\n洗乾淨的傷口<br />\n<br />\nTisept 洗傷口藥水 （黃色）<br />\n有洗傷口消毒功能外，還有清潔的功能，適合清洗含膿的傷口<br />\n適合沙石、泥地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cwbRB4t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcwbRB4t.png&h=3a2b23b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洗傷口方法<br />\n(1)消毒雙手，打開無菌敷料包<br />\n！切記打開時小心掂到無菌敷料包裡面！<br />\n(2)用鉗擺陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XTOkvrt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXTOkvrt.png&h=c9588c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(3)倒藥水落個盤啲紗布度，開始扭紗布 *盡量唔好咁濕啊*<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPjcmyd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPjcmyd.png&h=14ef531b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後開始洗傷口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YVNtEjZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYVNtEjZ.png&h=ea800df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(1)用藍色鉗夾乾淨紗布比黃色鉗，用黃色鉗洗傷口<br />\n！黃色鉗做污糟嘅鉗掂傷口，以免傷口受感染！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwusapV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwusapV.png&h=832de193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(2)洗傷口由內到外，轉圈360度洗 <br />\n！記得係360度，唔好用同一舊係咁兜圈洗傷口!<br />\n(3)用完就dum舊紗布<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4HmeRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4HmeRG.png&h=674d07fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(4)重複以上步驟<br />\n<br />\n如果大家唔知用幾多塊紗布既話？<br />\n以圖中既傷口作例子，洗內圍大概用3塊，洗外圍都係用3塊<br />\n<br />\n洗完傷口之後<br />\n(1)dum走黃色個隻鉗<br />\n(2)開無菌紗布，用藍色鉗夾2、3塊去印乾傷口<br />\n(3)剩下的紗布，用藍色鉗夾去放係傷口之上<br />\n(4)用Micropore痴實敷料<br />\n<br />\n洗眼方法<br />\n沖洗眼睛儘量有五分鐘<br />\n(1)用盛滿清水/生理鹽水的杯子洗眼<br />\n(2)直接在水喉下沖洗眼睛<br />\n！記得不停眨動眼睛，由於鹼性的化學品較易滲入眼球!<br />\n<br />\n如果要求診的話，記得把口生係你度，你咩都唔講都得嫁！<br />\n<br />\n發夢啊玩遊戲啊大家小心啲，學護仔係到希望幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}